{"tid":1346992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好失焦啊","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:06:03.000Z","uid":12574,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48015a6f3d40877bcb9bf7f66d7f1bc91611b0dc","tid":1346992,"uid":12574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"官商鄉黑呢招五年後再出<br />\n證明西環真係唔會再諗住回應五大訴求<br />\n並且尋求其他方法恐嚇大家唔好再上街<br />\n尋晚到今日已經冇人理過五大訴求<br />\n連上環開槍都冇人理<br />\n大家都係講727728光復元朗<br />\n情況嚴峻<br />\n唔可以比港共用呢招Distract<br />\n要港共成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n好話唔好聽<br />\n鄉黑再仆街 <br />\n我地依舊繼續狙擊柒婆<br />\n港共係逼於無奈要回應嘅<br />\n元朗還元朗<br />\n不要忘記反送中"},{"pid":"d250055e5c1370419083aa590116f21efce3d9ce","tid":1346992,"uid":39205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"幫手推，宜家係關鍵時期動搖淺藍民意！<br />\n<br />\n【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9be4aa49c006cd819765f45b5620ad93cf68cde4","tid":1346992,"uid":126420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41a52a91aea716b88cb69885e4c12f6867ab09cb","tid":1346992,"uid":42536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"兩睇，依家咁樣反而令班淺藍民意逆轉<br />\n呢個係好機會去傳遞訴求俾佢哋聽，佢哋依家會相對更願意聽<br />\n最緊要好好利用"},{"pid":"2e10b77528cb1f8de7122d801bb5a9026cfc970b","tid":1346992,"uid":12574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d1a7707f4ec7c7212a9379d6e25214f5139a556","tid":1346992,"uid":12574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a617cfa8e2e0df0c40d39f0ef13109ed0630cfa1","tid":1346992,"uid":12574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"敵人依舊係西環<br />\n依舊係柒婆<br />\n依舊係黑警<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放過佢地"},{"pid":"9a72aa40fe9ee3403eab06c6ea1ac9aec3b62